title: Miles Davis "Miles Runs the Voodoo Down" Live CD
description:
This is a live recording compilation of various Miles groups from the 60s and 70s. The audio quality is what&#039;s to be expected from a not large budget live recording in the 60s. Considering that it&#039;s excellent and the music of course is tremendous. 
Moon Records 1995.
Source: CD
MP3 files 192kb made with iTunes. 

Tracks: 
1.Autumn Leaves
2.Footprints
3.Shhh/Peaceful
4.Bitches Brew 
5.Miles Runs the Voodoo Down
6.Hush! 

1.Milano 1965 Miles w/Wayne, Herbie, Ron, Tony
2. Same band NYC 1966
3-5. Rome 1969 Miles w/Wayne, Chick, Dave and Jack
6. Rome 1972 Miles w/Gary Bartz, Keith, Michael Henderson, Ndugu, Don Alias and Mtume
